      <title>佩洛西敦促拜登退出后支持哈里斯担任总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/pelosi-endorses-fellow-bay-area-californian-harris-for-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南希·佩洛西 (Nancy Pelosi) 支持卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 担任总统，加入了民主党支持副总统竞选的浪潮，以填补这位前众议院议长帮助策划的空缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/pelosi-endorses-fellow-bay-area-californian-harris-for-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:25:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢旺达确认卡加梅以 99.2% 的得票率赢得压倒性胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/rwanda-confirms-kagame-s-landslide-win-with-99-2-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅以 99.2% 的选票获得第四个任期，延续其对这个东非国家二十五年的统治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/rwanda-confirms-kagame-s-landslide-win-with-99-2-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:12:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦奎尔和拉斯里支持哈里斯，华尔街“蜂巢”被解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/wall-street-s-khive-takes-shape-as-mcguire-lasry-back-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 正在迅速赢得金融界高层对她总统竞选的支持 - 并加入她的在线粉丝“KHive”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/wall-street-s-khive-takes-shape-as-mcguire-lasry-back-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将重要会议移出匈牙利以抗议奥尔班的外交政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/eu-moves-key-meeting-out-of-hungary-to-protest-orban-s-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟外交政策负责人表示，他计划将 8 月份的欧盟外交和防长会议从布达佩斯移至布鲁塞尔，以抗议维克托·奥尔班的外交行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/eu-moves-key-meeting-out-of-hungary-to-protest-orban-s-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持刀加拿大人遭以色列-加沙边界附近枪杀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/knife-wielding-canadian-shot-dead-near-israel-gaza-boundary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队和警方称，一名持刀的加拿大公民在加沙地带边界附近被以色列警卫开枪打死，这是一起罕见事件，可能与国际社会抗议巴勒斯坦领土战争有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/knife-wielding-canadian-shot-dead-near-israel-gaza-boundary</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:25:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年大选重启，哈里斯巩固民主党支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/harris-cements-democratic-support-as-2024-election-is-reset</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯迅速巩固了强大民主党人对她即将参加总统竞选的支持，努力结束党内动荡并改变唐纳德·特朗普必输的选举局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/harris-cements-democratic-support-as-2024-election-is-reset</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:20:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
