      <title>霍楚尔称纽约市最大的就业引擎已沦为“诈骗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ny-s-cdpap-home-health-aide-job-program-has-become-a-racket-hochul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约由医疗补助计划资助的家庭健康助理项目之一在地铁上打出广告称：“照顾你所爱的人，获得报酬”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ny-s-cdpap-home-health-aide-job-program-has-become-a-racket-hochul</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉称尚未决定新任巴西央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-he-still-has-to-agree-on-new-brazil-central-bank-head</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦表示，他和财政部长费尔南多·阿达德仍需就新央行行长人选达成一致，投资者正在考虑这一变化是否会改变该国的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-he-still-has-to-agree-on-new-brazil-central-bank-head</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉称马杜罗需要学习如何输掉选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦警告他的长期盟友尼古拉斯·马杜罗，委内瑞拉的经济未来取决于廉洁的选举，以确保政府在国际社会面前的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠特默和摩尔支持竞选，民主党人团结在哈里斯周围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/kamala-harris-endorsements-after-biden-drops-out-of-2024-race-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登退出竞选后，包括摇摆州州长、高级议员以及比尔和希拉里·克林顿在内的著名民主党人迅速支持卡马拉·哈里斯为该党的总统候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/kamala-harris-endorsements-after-biden-drops-out-of-2024-race-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
